{"tid":1786224,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英國央行：香港政局持續緊張　50 億美元撤資","createTime":"2019-12-17T03:47:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-17T06:44:11.000Z","uid":18354,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"4ac601f613c46f2803d6cb81d17bb9f1180d0b81","tid":1786224,"uid":18354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T03:47:52.000Z","msg":"英國中央銀行英倫銀行（Bank of England）發表金融穩定報告，指由於香港緊張政治局勢持續，自今年 4 月開始，至今累計已有約 50 億美元資金從香港的投資基金撤出，折合約 390 億港元。根據英倫銀行計算及 Refinitiv 和 EPFR Global 數據，上述數字相當於本港生產總值的 1.25%。<br />\n<br />\n彭博社又引述英資銀行滙豐控股和渣打集團指，由於本港示威活動加劇投資者憂慮，一些香港的富裕客戶決定在海外開設銀行賬戶。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/finance/%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E5%A4%AE%E8%A1%8C-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%94%BF%E5%B1%80%E6%8C%81%E7%BA%8C%E7%B7%8A%E5%BC%B5-50-%E5%84%84%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83%E6%92%A4%E8%B3%87/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Ffinance%2F%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25A4%25AE%25E8%25A1%258C-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25B1%2580%25E6%258C%2581%25E7%25BA%258C%25E7%25B7%258A%25E5%25BC%25B5-50-%25E5%2584%2584%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%2592%25A4%25E8%25B3%2587%2F&d=oGSqBYpvdEZZERTBUGrA0v8K46P7%2BXxs1F7ZCKkfkQw%3D&h=56535352\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Ffinance%2F%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25A4%25AE%25E8%25A1%258C-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25B1%2580%25E6%258C%2581%25E7%25BA%258C%25E7%25B7%258A%25E5%25BC%25B5-50-%25E5%2584%2584%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%2592%25A4%25E8%25B3%2587%2F&h=07d0f5b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/finance/%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E5%A4%AE%E8%A1%8C-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%94%BF%E5%B1%80%E6%8C%81%E7%BA%8C%E7%B7%8A%E5%BC%B5-50-%E5%84%84%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83%E6%92%A4%E8%B3%87/</a>"},{"pid":"61c04ad8b676fc8461fb24e8fc1145c2e19cf41d","tid":1786224,"uid":163704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T03:48